<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>10348</hymn_number>
<author>ʿạdl ḥbyb, ʿạdl ḥbyb</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - fyḍ ʿlyạ brwḥk yạlly sẖfytny bjrwḥk

[V2]
 yạlly wḥdk ʿzạyạ dạymạaⁿ ạmlạny brwḥk

[V3]
 1- fyḍ brwḥk ạrwy qlby ạlʿṭsẖạn yndẗ yrjʿ lyk

[V4]
 fyḍ brwḥk ạẓhr fyạ ạlạnsạn ạlly ṣnʿtẗ bạydyk

[V5]
 wạny lw ḥty knt ʿẓạm mtsẖttẗ qwẗ mn rwḥk tḥyy ạlqlwb ạlmytẗ

[V6]
 fyḍ ʿlyạ brwḥk ạrkʿ wạslm lyk

[V7]
 2- fyḍ brwḥk ạnhy wqt ạlnsyạn ʿlmny ạʿysẖ ạrḍyk

[V8]
 fyḍ brwḥk ʿly ḍʿyf ạlạymạn ybqy bṭl fy ạydyk

[V9]
 ạʿln fy ḥyạty dymạ mlkk hnạ wạn ạnt wḥdk syd kl ạrḍnạ

[V10]
 fyḍ ʿlyạ brwḥk ạsjd wạʿysẖ ạlyk

[V11]
 3- fyḍ brwḥk fy ḥyạẗ ạlạnsạn ạlkẖạṭy ạlly nạsyk

[V12]
 fyḍ brwḥk ytrk kl ạlạḥzạn yrjʿ yfrḥ byk

[V13]
 dh ạnt btḥsbnạ ạmnạ bʿd kẖyạntnạ bʿd ʿdm ạymạnạ bmwtk ḥbytnạ

[V14]
 fyḍ ʿlyạ brwḥk ḥyạty tkwn ạlyk

[V15]
 4- fyḍ brwḥk nskn rạḥẗ ạydk wrjạnạ mạ ykẖyb

[V16]
 fyḍ brwḥk tbqy qlwbnạ bytk wnḥml ạlṣlyb

[V17]
 ạbwạb qlwbnạ bdmk tkwn mtʿlmẗ bdmk qdsnạ yạlly mt ʿnnạ

[V18]
 fyḍ ʿlyạ brwḥk ạqbl ḥml ạlṣlyb</lyrics>
<title>fyḍ ʿlyạ brwḥk</title>
</song>